convert_counts <- function(x) {
  x <- ifelse(x > 0, 1, 0) 
  x <- factor(x, levels = c(0,1),
              label= c("Yes","No"))
  return(x)
}

Apply convert_counts

convert_train1 <- apply(matrix_train, MARGIN = 2, convert_counts)
convert_test1 <-apply(matrix_test, MARGIN = 2, convert_counts)
